{"tid":1940191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"給鍾意食甜蝦的妳","createTime":"2020-03-23T15:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T11:49:31.000Z","uid":305218,"like":39,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"92be7ef18aafda4a5fcd2526e66ee803341320bb","tid":1940191,"uid":305218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac開post<br />\n<br />\n  我係一個有抑鬱嘅人，上星期我個人去到臨界點，好想放低哂所有野死左佢（包括佢），所以我同佢講咗分手，但到我個人冷靜返之後，我好後悔，我知道我係唔值得原諒，對唔住。<br />\n  <br />\n我同你識咗差唔多三年，三年黎同你已經錯過咗好多嘅機會，到今次好難得先一齊到，我好唔捨得你，我仲係好愛你，我好想再同你一齊去食放題，好想再同你去周圍玩，好想再見到你笑好想再聽到你叫我個名，我已經有聽你話去覆診，我已經飲小咗酒，我有咩我都可以改架，可唔可以原諒我？比多一次機會我同你一齊？<br />\n<br />\n我知道我好廢好on9，如果想屌我就屌，唔洗留力，但希望大家集氣正評支持我，推到佢見到，感激！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n送多一首歌比妳，好耐以前你話鍾意我唱呢首歌，唔知你記唔記得<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_vrPoLRN2U0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_vrPoLRN2U0&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=b53876a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_vrPoLRN2U0</a>"},{"pid":"63d2a260717130e334fae6ae732999e5a50adb25","tid":1940191,"uid":122590,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"關我撚事？"},{"pid":"bdf051e718938e942420f7eb08e337293828fedb","tid":1940191,"uid":305218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d2a260717130e334fae6ae732999e5a50adb25","tid":1940191,"uid":122590,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"關我撚事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c1b5ddb88641f83ccc4d25fcdf1566f14ba470","tid":1940191,"uid":431,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"我要食甜蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46144c8f63c9a095b69c4ec1cc6